<DOCNO> NYT19990428.0105 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-28 13:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6358 &Cx1f; tad-z
a p &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TECH-POLITICS-$ADV050     04-28 1100
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TECH-POLITICS-$ADV0502-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    PRESIDENTIAL CANDIDATES FIND GOLD IN HIGH TECHNOLOGY
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington, (f) financial and (p) political
categories
 &HT;    With contribution chart at end of story
