</P>
<P>
   WOM-NOTEBOOK (Undated) -- A new series on Lifetime Television is
tackling women's sports issues. The segments are already drawing a
response akin to male-dominated sports talk radio. By Barbara
Huebner.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
