<P>
   SWEAT LODGE-JAIL &QL;
</P>
<P>
   COMANCHE, Texas _ The sight of a sweat lodge in Comanche County
probably wouldn't have been unusual back in the 1800s. But since
few Native Americans are left in the region, and its location is
inside the grounds of the Comanche County Jail, the lodge now is a
little out of the ordinary. By BILL HANNA. Story has moved in ``a''
general news category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   L I F E S T Y L E &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   SMART LOVE-PARENTING &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Forget potty training and letting your newborn cry
himself to sleep. Forget timeouts and spankings. And for heaven's
sake, forget tough love. Want happier and more caring children?
Forget discipline altogether and apply smart love, a new and
controversial alternative to rigid discipline and the unstructured
permissiveness that has dominated child-rearing since the '60s. By
GRACIE BONDS STAPLES. Story has moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
