<P>
   Q: What do you get when you cross a monkey with a sheep?
</P>
<P>
   A: A Baaboon! Lacey Espree.
</P>
<P>
   Q: Where do puppy dogs get their tails?
</P>
<P>
   A: From the re-tail store! Kendra Newton.
</P>
<P>
   Q: Hey Joe, why are you carrying that piano on your back?
</P>
<P>
   A: I want to carry a tune. Nicki Sauls.
</P>
<P>
   Q: What do you call a sleeping bull?
</P>
<P>
   A: A bulldozer. Christina Newton.
</P>
<P>
   Q: How did the telephone propose to his girlfriend?
</P>
<P>
   A: He gave her a ring. Tandie Loyd.
