<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-28 19:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6953 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HERBERT-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      04-28 0735
