technologies company, is moving its headquarters from Beverly Hills
to suburban Woodland Hills in the San Fernando Valley area of Los
Angeles next month. By Enrique Rivero. (Will move in the ``f''
financial news file.)
</P>
<P>
   WELLPOINT-EARNINGS (Thousand Oaks, Calif.) _ Health insurer
Wellpoint Health Networks Inc. nailed analysts' first-quarter
earnings estimates Wednesday but reported a 19 percent drop in
out-of-state membership. By Ben Sullivan. (Will move in the ``f''
financial news file.)
</P>
