   SOCIAL-SECURITY (Washington) _ Despite Republican congressional
leaders' word that an overhaul of Social Security will not be
considered this year, House Ways and Means Committee Chairman Bill
Archer, R-Texas, lays out his proposal. By BENNETT ROTH. (Already
filed.)
</P>
