   (NYT12) NEW YORK -- April 28, 1999 -- MOON-THEATER-REVIEW, 4-28
-- Marian Seldes and Toby Stephens in ``Ring Round the Moon.'' This
1947 play, the story of one perversely enchanted evening of a grand
ball, is equal parts preciousness and cynicism. It is the sort of
