Karen Long, a counselor with the Arapahoe County Sheriff's Victim
Assistance program, at the family home on Wednesday. Isaiah Shoels
was singled out and shot to death last week not only for being an
athlete but also for being black. (Monica Almeida/New York Times
Photo) LITE
</P>
<P>
   (NYT5) NEW YORK -- April 28, 1999 -- DESIGN-PRINCESS-2, 4-28 --
New designs by Ingegerd Raman for Skruf show the austere, Nordic
side of Swedish esthetics. Sweden's Princess Christina has spent
the last 10 years promoting design in the hopes of establishing a
museum in Stockholm. (Tony Cenicola/New York Times Photo)
