reporters about the situation in Kosovo on Wednesday. Clinton will
travel to Germany next Tuesday to visit U.S. troops supporting the
NATO air campaign in Yugoslavia, the White House announced on
Wednesday. (Paul Hosefros/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT12) NEW YORK -- April 28, 1999 -- MOON-THEATER-REVIEW, 4-28
-- Marian Seldes and Toby Stephens in ``Ring Round the Moon.'' This
1947 play, the story of one perversely enchanted evening of a grand
ball, is equal parts preciousness and cynicism. It is the sort of
work that makes you say, if you're feeling charitable, ``Oh, those
worldly, romantic French.'' (Sara Krulwich/New York Times Photo)
